DESCRIPTION:THE FUTURE AGENCY OPPORTUNITY: What Top Agents Are Doing Next\n\nAgency Solutions LIVE | Wednesday\, May 20\, 2026 | 3:00 PM Eastern\n\nThe landscape is shifting. The agents who win the next five years won't be the ones who wait to see how things settle. They'll be the ones already moving.\n\nFive Presidents Club agents — Al Shattuck\, David Peterson\, Karen Burtis\, Jeff Burtis\, and Hayk Tadevosyan — for an unfiltered\, live-only conversation about what's actually changing\, what it means for your book\, and the moves they're making right now.\n\nWhat you'll walk away with:\n• Live reactions from 5 Presidents Club agents\n• What the changes actually mean financially\n• Where top agents see the real opportunity\n• Operational pivots you can make NOW\n• Q&A with agents already preparing for what's next\n\nLIVE ONLY. No recording. No replay. You must be there.\n\nJoin via Microsoft Teams:\nhttps://teams.microsoft.com/meet/287597241544189?p=rEVXyWaT9Ufl74Eq4W\n\nMeeting ID: 287 597 241 544 189\nPasscode: pG66ts6u\n\nConnecting Agents – Inspiring Greatness\nAgency Network
